Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.57,0:22:29.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}一定都能变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:32.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}Little Lion Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:43.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}心情如脱缰疾驰的骏马
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:45.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}无论多大的危机都能跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:46.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}一定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:47.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}会让你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:47.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}很快就
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:48.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}拥抱幸福与自由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:51.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}不再让你不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:53.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}我暧昧弱小的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:56.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}有超越极限的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:22:57.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:22:58.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}哪怕现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:22:58.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}对你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:22:59.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}信号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:02.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}时刻做好捕捉的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:06.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}对我来说你比谁都重要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.99,0:23:08.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}内心在发烫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:13.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}来吧 以这颗心去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:17.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}你的梦想 明天和未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:20.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}我绝对都会亲手去守护
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:23.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}并为此发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:28.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,170)}我会陪伴你为你拭去眼泪
